Ref: https://www.sohamkamani.com/nodejs/jwt-authentication/
JWT generate: https://github.com/auth0/node-jsonwebtoken → npm i jsonwebtoken  

In order to create a JSON web token, we will need — three things:

1. Payload
2. Secret (Private key)
3. Signing options

Step 1:  Created Secret (Private key) -> Có thể tạo primary key bất kỳ lưu ở server → Càng phức tạp càng tốt

 → https://travistidwell.com/jsencrypt/demo/ → generate public key and private key → save it into two files
 
 
 
